## Reduced from 25 → 16 Rules

**Consolidations Made:**
- **Database Rules** (5 → 1): Combined data-cleanup, database-maintenance, database-migrations, database-performance, schema-evolution into `@database-management.mdc`
- **Utility Rules** (3 → 1): Combined utilities, environment-variables, notes into `@project-utilities.mdc`  
- **Frontend Rules** (3 → 1): Combined nextjs-best-practices, react-best-practices, hooks into `@frontend-framework.mdc`

**Benefits:**
- 40% reduction in cognitive load
- Eliminated overlap and duplication
- Improved logical grouping
- Maintained specialization where needed
- Added comprehensive integration system rule